reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Travel Transformed: Unparalleled Organization Meets Space Efficiency!
reviews.reviewText: If you’re a traveler, frequent or not, these 8-Piece Deluxe Compression Packing Cubes are an absolute game-changer. From the moment I unboxed them, I could tell they were crafted with precision and designed with the traveler's needs in mind.Maximized Space - The hybrid design allows for optimal compression, letting me fit more into my suitcase than ever before. I was genuinely surprised at how much space I saved.Organization Dream - Each cube serves a unique purpose and size, making it effortless to segregate clothes, accessories, toiletries, and more. Gone are the days of rummaging through my suitcase to find that one elusive sock!Sturdy and Durable - Despite the lightweight feel, these cubes are incredibly durable. The zippers glide smoothly, and the material feels robust, ensuring that these will be a travel companion for many trips to come.Visual Appeal - They're not just functional; they look great too! The aesthetic design makes it a pleasure to open up my luggage each time.Travel Stress Reducer - Packing and unpacking used to be one of my most dreaded travel tasks. These cubes have made it so much simpler and stress-free. I now find packing almost therapeutic!In summary, the 8-Piece Deluxe Compression Packing Cubes are a worthy investment for anyone looking to maximize space and minimize hassle. Whether you’re embarking on a weekend getaway or a month-long journey, these cubes will ensure that you do so with elegance and efficiency. Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pleasantly surprised of the Great Sizes
reviews.reviewText: We have purchased from other stores many of these. Everything has been too thin and too small to fit in a large suitcase for travelling abroad. This is the first set that actually fills a large suitcase on one side and half on the other with room for tuckin extra stuff. I was pleasantly surprised that the large set has zippers that exspand for twice their size. The vibrant colors are fun. Don't purchase ones that are half the price. They do not hold up and They give you so many little sizes it doesn't really help with packing larger items. Pleasantly surprised.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great travel organizer to use on regular basis.
reviews.reviewText: Got this to use on my regular work travel to keep stuff organized. Definitely helps keep different clothing and toiletries separate. The pack has enough cubes to keep a carry on luggage on local travel organized. If you going for few week internationally will recommend buying 2 more packs which I did and use it when i go on outside the country. The cubes doesn't compress the clothing articles as i thought it would but enough to fit little more stuff and also mainly for organizational purposes.Pros: 1) Very light weight. 2) Different size mix. 3) 8 Pack enough to keep everything organized on carry on luggageCons: 1) Not as much compression as i thought.Overall: Definitely a good quality material cubes to keep and use on regular basis to keep everything organized and definitely happy with the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent quality and exceptional customer service
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely LOVE Well Traveled Gear 8-piece Deluxe Compression Packing Cubes. I bought 2 sets - one for my husband and one for me. We had previously owned another packing cube sets purchased through Amazon but the quality was not great and the cubes were flimsy and loose when they are not completely filled. I decided we need packing cubes that can compress as well so that our clothing stay compact and neat and will save space in our luggage at the same time. Well Traveled Gear's packing cubes met our expectations in every way!!Besides being very happy with their products, I would like to commend on their exceptional customer service. There was an issue with our packages when they first arrived. I reached out to Well Traveled Gear through email. I was very nicely surprised that Nympha from Well Traveled Gear responded to my email shortly after. I was surprised by her prompt response because I had sent the email at night. It was past business hours and I wasn't expecting a response till the next day. Nimpha addressed the issue immediately. She was very kind and went over and beyond to rectify the issue straight away. I have never experienced such outstanding customer service before!! I am truly impressed and have shared my experience with my friends.I highly recommend Well Traveled Gear products and I will definitely purchase more traveling products from them when the need arises again.
